    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスに会ったのは、
１度きりだったんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Were you shocked after you first met Dhaos?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの後、何度も
あいつ探して森の中を巡った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>After that encounter I searched for him in the forest.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43316</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でもね、呼べど探せど、
あいつ姿を現さなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But no matter how much I'd search or call out for him, he'd simply not show up.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、それっきり？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's where it ends?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43500</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それがね、さんざん探して、
もういないのかなって思って</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right. I searched very very thoroughly but there was no trace of him left.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>疲れ果てて森の切り株を枕に眠って、
目を覚ましたら、そばにあいつがいて星を見てるの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I got so exhausted I took a nap on a tree stump. When I opened my eyes he was close to me, stargazing.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あっ……それって前にしてた
“北の真ん中星”の話ですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's where you learnt about the Northern Middle Star!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう！　覚えてたんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes! You remembered about it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの時は、まさかダオスの話だって
知らなかったから興味本位で聞いてて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At that time I didn't know you were talking about Dhaos, of course, but it was a very touching story.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今は興味本位じゃない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And you think it's no longer touching now?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……あ、そのぉ……今も興味本位、かな……
……あっ！　ちょっとだけ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y—yes! It's still an interesting story!! Well, I think...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_100_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いいよ。もっと聞かせてあげるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine. Then I'll teach you more things.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
